PrecisAuthority to amend the TR'ONDËK HWËCH'IN SELF-GOVERNMENT AGREEMENT to empower them to enact laws relating to the implementation of measures made pursuant to any taxation agreement with the Minister of Finance and provide them with a GST refund paid by its government when performing its functions, effective November 1, 2000.
Attachments
precis:
Authority to amend the TR'ONDËK HWËCH'IN SELF-GOVERNMENT AGREEMENT to
empower them to enact laws relating to the implementation of measures made
pursuant to any taxation agreement with the Minister of Finance and provide
them with a GST refund paid by its government when performing its
functions, effective November 1, 2000.
